TKV\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ATKV\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ATKV\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympic Games 2024 experience\", \"from\": 561, \"to\": 600}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Retirement is always a deeply personal decision for any athlete, and no one could say that Smith has not achieved greatness.\", \"from\": 633, \"to\": 757, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Retirement\", \"from\": 633, \"to\": 643}, {\"ngram\": \"a deeply personal decision\", \"from\": 654, \"to\": 680}, {\"ngram\": \"any athlete\", \"from\": 685, \"to\": 696}, {\"ngram\": \"no one\", \"from\": 702, \"to\": 708}, {\"ngram\": \"Smith\", \"from\": 724, \"to\": 729}, {\"ngram\": \"greatness\", \"from\": 747, \"to\": 756}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She steps off the podium as the greatest Olympian produced by South Africa with two gold medals and two silvers.\", \"from\": 759, \"to\": 871, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 800, \"end\": 808, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999840442798, \"rank\": 1.5955856349660668e-08, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 821, \"end\": 833, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 3.087871280697648e-13, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the podium\", \"from\": 773, \"to\": 783}, {\"ngram\": \"two gold medals\", \"from\": 839, \"to\": 854}, {\"ngram\": \"two silvers\", \"from\": 859, \"to\": 870}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Only a breath and a heartbeat stood between her and all four of her medals being gold,\\\" said McKenzie.\", \"from\": 873, \"to\": 976, \"entities\": [],